om/daily-ratings/tuesday-final-ratings-oct-15-2019/|archive-date=October 23, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| end8             = January 28, 2020\n| endrating8       = 0.73<ref name=\"8.10\">{{cite web|url=https://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/tuesday-final-ratings-jan-28-2020/|title='This is Us' adjusts up, 'Arrow' adjusts down: Tuesday final ratings|last=Welch|first=Alex|work=TV by the Numbers|date=January 29, 2020|accessdate=January 29, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129214435/https://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/tuesday-final-ratings-jan-28-2020/|archive-date=January 29, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| season8          = 2019\u201320\n| rank8            = \n| viewers8         = \n| 18_49_rating8    = \n}}\n\n===Accolades===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:99%;\"\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Award\n! scope=\"col\" | Category\n! scope=\"col\" | Nominee(s)\n! scope=\"col\" | Result\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{Abbr|Ref.|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | 2012\n| [[IGN Awards]]\n| Best TV Hero\n| data-sort-value=\"Amell, Stephen\" | [[Oliver Queen (Arrowverse)|Oliver Queen]] ([[Stephen Amell]])\n| {{Nom}}\n| <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ign.com/wikis/best-of-2012/Best_TV_Hero |title=2012 IGN Best TV Hero |website=IGN.com |publisher=[[Ziff Davis]] |access-date=June 23, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722200139/http://www.ign.com/wikis/best-of-2012/Best_TV_Hero |archive-date=July 22, 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[17th Satellite Awards|Satellite Awards]]\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Television Series&nbsp;\u2013 Genre]]\n| data-sort-value=\"Arrow\" | ''Arrow''\n| {{Nom}}\n| <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pressacademy.com/award_cat/2012/ |title=2012 |website=pressacademy.com |publisher=[[International Press Academy]] |access-date=June 23, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322225104/http://ww